{"tid":1586533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警帶少量冰毒及偉哥過境被截獲　求情稱為止痛　官押後判","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:06:52.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7999c5f1c91c9a5e01035157a22d0147606022","tid":1586533,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3311395/org/9f5dae9882ffe9e3bd8f8083e27f2df0.jpg/4kVKfukifIiIdxAw2DaQ1t1qRoIdU4m7vPpCQLz6QkA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3311395%2Forg%2F9f5dae9882ffe9e3bd8f8083e27f2df0.jpg%2F4kVKfukifIiIdxAw2DaQ1t1qRoIdU4m7vPpCQLz6QkA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f7c861d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n休班警員在羅湖過關時被搜出冰毒、偉哥、私煙等，今（20日）於粉嶺法院承認承認藏毒、管有應課稅品等4罪。辯方求情指他3年前任交通警執勤期間滑倒受傷，受朋友慫恿下首次嘗試以毒品減輕痛楚，惟裁判官指出他似乎已吸毒一段時間。裁判官將判刑押後至下月9日，以待索取感化官報告。被告續准保釋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3310529/org/185c1beef06b74dc65bc2e201cfd6b31.jpg/ET4tEhvLn4ROz_S9O_ngPfI3Yn2Lt_dFl_7Q1Zf-0NU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3310529%2Forg%2F185c1beef06b74dc65bc2e201cfd6b31.jpg%2FET4tEhvLn4ROz_S9O_ngPfI3Yn2Lt_dFl_7Q1Zf-0NU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2ab72e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告馬道宸在粉嶺法院承認管有危險藥物等罪名。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n被告馬道宸（47歲），被控於4月8日在羅湖管制站海關入境大堂管有一顆含昔多芬的藥物、小量冰毒，以及適用於及擬用作於吸服危險藥物的器具，即玻璃管、膠樽等物品。他另被指未有向海關人員申報行李內的238支未完稅香煙。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告原本為交通警，3年前因垃圾車漏出的水滑倒在地，傷及頸椎，之後轉作文職。被告在意外後常要止痛，但認為醫生處方的止痛藥效果有限，在友人慫恿下首次服食冰毒。裁判官質問為何被告攜毒品過關，聽到辯方指他純粹隨手放入背包帶回家後，再問：「即係慣咗？」辯方則強調此案屬初犯。裁判官又道，會視乎被告能否自願戒毒，再決定要否將他收柙以接受強制戒毒。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC2954/2019<br />\n撰文：林樂兒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/377607/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%B8%B6%E5%B0%91%E9%87%8F%E5%86%B0%E6%AF%92%E5%8F%8A%E5%81%89%E5%93%A5%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83%E8%A2%AB%E6%88%AA%E7%8D%B2-%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E7%A8%B1%E7%82%BA%E6%AD%A2%E7%97%9B-%E5%AE%98%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F377607%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%25B0%2591%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2586%25B0%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2593%25A5%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2588%25AA%25E7%258D%25B2-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E7%2597%259B-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2588%25A4&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=e0cb0a68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/377607/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%B8%B6%E5%B0%91%E9%87%8F%E5%86%B0%E6%AF%92%E5%8F%8A%E5%81%89%E5%93%A5%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83%E8%A2%AB%E6%88%AA%E7%8D%B2-%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E7%A8%B1%E7%82%BA%E6%AD%A2%E7%97%9B-%E5%AE%98%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%88%A4</a>"}]}